<blockquote>
  <p>Noticed now we now define <code class="highlighter-rouge">inductive</code> in a mixed style: 
some arg is before <code class="highlighter-rouge">:</code> (named), some are after <code class="highlighter-rouge">:</code> (anonymous).</p>
</blockquote>

<p>We could do this as well</p>

