<h2 id="commands-statement">Commands (Statement)</h2>

<pre><code class="language-bnf">c ::= SKIP | x ::= a | c ;; c | TEST b THEN c ELSE c FI | WHILE b DO c END
</code></pre>

<blockquote>
  <p>we use <code class="highlighter-rouge">TEST</code> to avoid conflicting with the <code class="highlighter-rouge">if</code> and <code class="highlighter-rouge">IF</code> notations from the standard library.</p>
</blockquote>

